description: Milky Way from the Lion Rock to the Blue Pool at Piha Beach - Piha is one of the most gorgeous black-sand beaches on the rugged coast west of Auckland. It provides many incredible walks, and it is a perfect place for surfers. So back in October we had the amazing possibility to visit this place and shoot the night sky. With some very bad weather in the beginning, the wait was totally worth it...
